{"tid":117240,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]啲仆街係公屋養狗點搞好？","createTime":"2017-02-12T05:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T01:40:58.000Z","uid":78237,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ced0e198ace6ed13759c04fba100b0b3984eaa2","tid":117240,"uid":78237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"公屋明明唔比養狗<br />\n03年一次性豁免過個派狗到宜家都應該死得七七八八，<br />\n但係呢幾年呢死仆街越黎越多人養狗，<br />\n前幾日送女朋友番屋企，<br />\n一開lift門，<br />\n有對mk情侶拖住兩隻大雪橇狗，仲要臭到仆街，<br />\n因為太臭我地唔想入lift，<br />\n跟住對死mk竟然話：「怕狗可以唔入黎」<br />\n<br />\n我當堂呆咗，<br />\n佢地竟然可以惡到咁。<br />\n<br />\n到底點搞好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b0534aab036d16e04d3d35a341a0018a58c244","tid":117240,"uid":78237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲教路點處理，<br />\n已經同個區議員講咗要佢加多啲banner講扣五分個啲"},{"pid":"623d27be0fb38ea591b81b88b7dbd4cbbbdae474","tid":117240,"uid":69987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"你唔洗再住公屋咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceca6694fd559dffe43121f79ab3266e257637cb","tid":117240,"uid":78237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔洗再住公屋咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n那有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7900eb90f52ad036ccc809d5153f1c3eae7f36a1","tid":117240,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4baa9ce23222ef643ea0c94e87456c1c26ebacd3","tid":117240,"uid":78237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你條傻仔唔睇埋佢住邊層邊個單位投訴</blockquote><br />\n個一剎那嘅感覺係<br />\n臭&gt;呆&gt;門已閂"},{"pid":"8f5d260fdd98910